{"id":"49e56a2847f4e062d42d41a2cc198d39df38966baa0075e68b3d6802bd9c7d2d","item_id":"cc08ae9257:0","text":"RenderManStudio_Lighting_v01.hip"}
{"id":"d7c7c243dec65424dd5732c932ded48434f472a308fbff0e3183e24f9e4ed14d","item_id":"cc08ae9257:1","text":"此场景是 Solaris 管线的末端，也是"}
{"id":"bb167a03c268df93d67d9034f0a59a39e4af995662d361c42bbdeafed9dac52d","item_id":"cc08ae9257:2","text":"$HIP/usd/Layout/RenderManStudio_Layout_v1.usda"}
{"id":"0c2806fb5d2dffbdebac765d852727c98fe6cce49d5b0414df8f3d15cf7e11cf","item_id":"cc08ae9257:3","text":"文件被加载的位置。"}
{"id":"9cc475e1dc6a5b943225b39e8f7fec6c6e11a394d9f471f485b78238ad5cca39","item_id":"cc08ae9257:4","text":"从 stage（舞台）中可以看到，已经设置了若干 lights（灯光），方便你开始使用。"}
{"id":"262121c5372be8af3ae6ff0d3d138d9e6e1249335222c7f0e02535e35073bb0b","item_id":"cc08ae9257:5","text":"edit"}
{"id":"14ee59f2f489fe048a0342471e4764660f524b2c6dd63cc79bd9ce565981f981","item_id":"cc08ae9257:6","text":"节点用于最终 layout（布局）微调，并且也已添加 close camera（近景摄影机）和 wide camera（广角摄影机）。"}
{"id":"58f911693e82d3aefe44b8fd116df762fe9576609c07e5912935eab0089ee722","item_id":"cc08ae9257:7","text":"为了增加真实感，还包含一个 procedural fog setup（程序化雾设置）；fog thickness（雾厚度）和 fog height（雾高度）可以通过位于"}
{"id":"5eee68cd689b7cff639ad922d0e35ba77b8c8debe06ca319e85ac8b38554adff","item_id":"cc08ae9257:8","text":"sopcreate_Volume"}
{"id":"545ea538461003efdc8c81c244531b003f6f26cfccf6c0073b3239fdedf49446","item_id":"cc08ae9257:9","text":"节点上的 2 个 promoted parameters（提升参数）轻松控制。"}
{"id":"3955a87e78743cfe7b78b0544ce957c38e97c3b6ce26f2ad18d4b2cc26e4ce13","item_id":"cc08ae9257:10","text":"已经设置好两台 camera（摄影机）。"}
{"id":"6c0acc5d4bc7c05fe2d9bd5c98e44aa5f8ae88eb0f4241f10f152aa4e6dff9fa","item_id":"cc08ae9257:11","text":"/RenderManStudio/CAM/RenderCam_wide_35mm"}
{"id":"1dc71cd270924e454b316d42adb68d1f04e0a69b90bcd6254dd20bdcbc703130","item_id":"cc08ae9257:12","text":"/RenderManStudio/CAM/RenderCam_Close_85mm"}
{"id":"779bc2e0dc6221de64618b8a67f49b22b7b50bfc25a598e4c617cce571291723","item_id":"cc08ae9257:13","text":"场景已经全部设置好，可用于渲染 wide camera（广角摄影机）和 close camera（近景摄影机）... 我们甚至还设置了 denoising（降噪）！"}
